Package sample.datamodel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    The Actor class represents an actor
    ActorData
    Singleton class that stores the data of an actor into a Hashmap for later access.
    DataOrganisation
    Singleton class that holds information about the directors, actors and genres of each movie.
    Director
    The Director class represents a director.
    DirectorData
    Singleton class that stores the data of a director into a Hashmap for later access.
    Movie
    The Movie class represents a move.
    MovieData
    Singleton class stores the data of all the movies in an observable list.
    NonRegisteredUser
    Class to improve understandability of object model.
    NonRegisteredUserData
    Singleton class that stores the data of a of all Nonregistered Users into a List for later access.
    RecommendationHandler
    Purpose of this class is to handle the logic for recommending movies based on the user preferences.
    RegisteredUser
    The RegisteredUser class represents a user that is registered.
    RegisteredUserData
    Singleton class that stores the data of a of all Registered Users into a Map for later access and in interactive mode it holds information which user is currently logged in.
